on that screen?

07:43.296 --> 07:44.421
Pretty clear. Heh.

07:44.589 --> 07:47.132
Do I look like l feel better?

07:48.259 --> 07:51.428
I mean, it's not, like, HD quality.

07:52.096 --> 07:55.432
Listen, you're gonna talk to your mother
and you're gonna fix this.

07:55.600 --> 07:58.518
Or that thing l said I was gonna do to you
when you got home...

07:58.728 --> 08:01.104
...you can do to yourself.

08:03.441 --> 08:06.485
Like he's been doing since he got here.

08:09.530 --> 08:11.615
[SOFT MUSlC PLAYING OVER SPEAKERS]

08:11.782 --> 08:14.826
Sheldon, this place is so romantic.

08:14.994 --> 08:17.954
Aw.... l'm glad you like it. Raj picked it out.

08:19.749 --> 08:21.875
When you see him,
tell him l say thank you.

08:22.043 --> 08:23.543
Tell him yourself.

08:24.462 --> 08:26.963
Yoo-hoo! Over here.

08:29.133 --> 08:31.510
I don't understand. What's he doing here?

08:31.677 --> 08:34.804
-I invited him.
-On our date?

08:34.972 --> 08:36.556
Sheldon, that's not okay.

08:36.724 --> 08:41.144
Oh. Yes, it is. There's a loophole
in the relationship agreement.

08:41.354 --> 08:42.854
You found a loophole?

08:45.525 --> 08:47.859
Sorry I started without you...

08:48.027 --> 08:51.530
...I'm a little nervous.
It's been a long time since I've been on a date.

08:52.406 --> 08:55.367
I can't believe
I bleached my mustache for this.

08:55.535 --> 08:59.162
You should go to my girl,
she'll knock out those sideburns for free.

09:06.420 --> 09:10.382
You know, Amy, l don't think
you and l have had a real conversation.

09:10.550 --> 09:13.218
Let's use tonight
to get to know each other better.

09:14.178 --> 09:15.554
You start.

09:18.683 --> 09:19.933
Go home.

09:21.018 --> 09:23.436
-I don't understand.
-Sheldon, how could you do this?

09:23.604 --> 09:26.731
-It's our second anniversary.
-It's your anniversary?

09:27.441 --> 09:29.859
Oh, my God, I had no idea.

09:30.194 --> 09:32.237
Amy, please, let me make this right.

09:32.822 --> 09:34.781
-Thank you.
-My pleasure. Waiter?

09:34.949 --> 09:37.742
A bottle of champagne
and three glasses.

09:38.703 --> 09:41.580
Oh, boy, isn't this romantic?

09:42.081 --> 09:46.084
I hope that's a rhetorical question
because l have no clue.

09:48.421 --> 09:50.589
Mm. This is great, what's the occasion?

09:50.756 --> 09:53.967
No occasion.
Things have been a little weird between us...

09:54.135 --> 09:56.720
...so l wanted to throw together
a fun night for you.

09:56.887 --> 09:58.805
-That is so sweet.
-I got your favorites:

09:58.973 --> 10:03.226
Beer, wings, sliders, we can watch
the football game. I even painted my stomach.

10:06.063 --> 10:08.315
-Go sports?
-Well?

10:08.482 --> 10:11.943
In case you were in the mood for baseball,
I didn't wanna look ridiculous.

10:12.653 --> 10:15.447
-This is awesome, l love it.
-Good, l'm glad.

10:15.615 --> 10:17.949
I worked my ass off,
so this is what l needed.

10:18.159 --> 10:21.161
Great, just relax and enjoy.
Tonight is all about you.

10:21.370 --> 10:22.787
Ah. Thank you.

10:23.205 --> 10:24.623
[CHUCKLES]

10:24.790 --> 10:26.291
[SlGHS]

10:26.459 --> 10:29.085
So where exactly are we
in this relationship?

10:30.630 --> 10:33.465
Oh, come on, l just told you
I had a hard day.

10:33.633 --> 10:36.635
-You're right, l'm sorry. Let's watch the game.
-Great.

10:37.053 --> 10:38.803
[SlGHS]

10:38.971 --> 10:42.682
Just know, the longer we wait
to talk about it the weirder it gets.

10:43.476 --> 10:46.603
Sweetie, can l just be the girl tonight?

10:46.979 --> 10:49.147
Absolutely. You're the girl, l'm the guy.

10:49.774 --> 10:52.317
Watch your football game
while l make you a plate here.

10:52.485 --> 10:53.943
Thank you.

10:54.945 --> 10:56.279
[KNOCKING ON DOOR]

10:56.447 --> 10:59.282
I'll get it. Go sports! Heh.

11:01.160 --> 11:03.286
Hello-lo-lo.

11:04.205 --> 11:06.373
I thought you were out
with Sheldon and Amy.

11:06.540 --> 11:09.959
I was, but it's their anniversary,
and I didn't wanna be a third wheel...

11:10.127 --> 11:13.004
...so l figured I'd hang out
with you and Penny on your date.

11:13.839 --> 11:17.467
It's not really a great time.
Penny and l have some things to talk about.

11:17.635 --> 11:19.052
PENNY:
No we don't, come on in!

11:19.970 --> 11:21.805
Sweet.

11:22.139 --> 11:25.058
I can't believe
I shaved my stomach for this.

11:30.731 --> 11:32.691
DlMITRl:
Hey, Froot Loops.

11:36.362 --> 11:38.029
You got a phone call.

11:38.447 --> 11:39.739
Who is it?

11:39.949 --> 11:43.868
A woman who says she's your mother
but sounds like your father.

11:47.039 --> 11:48.081
[TURNS SPEAKER ON]

11:48.249 --> 11:49.541
Hey, Ma.

11:49.709 --> 11:53.503
You know, we could see each other
if you turn on the computer.

11:53.671 --> 11:55.755
MRS. WOLOWlTZ:
I'm not going near that fakakta thing.

11:55.965 --> 11:58.466
I'll catch a computer virus!

11:59.844 --> 12:02.887
