something important to tell me.

12:15.693 --> 12:18.570
Okay, here it is:

12:19.029 --> 12:23.074
Bernadette and l
are starting a life together.

12:23.242 --> 12:24.367
-And--
-Ohff God.

12:24.535 --> 12:26.202
