12:26.370 --> 12:28.413
-Ma--
-It's okay.

12:28.706 --> 12:30.874
Your father left me, you left me.

12:31.041 --> 12:34.919
I guess l'm just the kind of person
people like to leave.

12:37.214 --> 12:41.134
It's not definite. l'll talk to Bernadette.

12:41.302 --> 12:42.385
Don't bother.

12:42.553 --> 12:47.056
