-Yeah, it's fun, isn't it?
-Well...

13:33.854 --> 13:38.650
...it's not the balls-to-the-wall action
of badminton or cricket, but hey...

13:39.193 --> 13:40.693
...what is?

13:42.154 --> 13:43.655
Who's ready for another beer?

13:43.823 --> 13:45.073
-I'm good.
-No, thank you.

13:45.616 --> 13:46.991
Girls.

13:48.118 --> 13:50.829
I am having the nicest time.

13:50.996 --> 13:53.623
You guys are like family to me.
You know that, right?

13:53.791 --> 13:55.500
That's great. Get out.

13:56.335 --> 13:59.838
-What? Why?
-Penny and l have some issues to talk about.

14:00.005 --> 14:02.966
Oh, pish on your issues.

14:03.801 --> 14:05.510
You guys are fine.

14:05.803 --> 14:08.221
Yes, you've had some bumps
along the way.

14:08.389 --> 14:11.724
I mean, Penny, you've always known
how this man has felt about you.

14:11.892 --> 14:14.185
